Clone current repository
git clone https://github.com/dmst-sweng/git-intro.git

Create a new branch name 'theosotr'
git checkout -b theosotr

A new commit which fixes code allignent of ExcitingStory class
git commit -a -m "Fix code alligment"

Add Changelog_theosotr file under version control
git add Changelog_theosotr

Create a new commit which adds Changelog_theosotr file
git commit -m "Add Changelog_theosotr file"

Push branch 'theosotr' to the upstream repository
git push origin theosotr

Go to master branch
git checkout master

Merge branch 'theosotr' into master branch
git merge theosotr

Push changes to the upstream repository
git push origin master

Go to 'theosotr' branch
git checkout theosotr

Create a new commit which fixes code alignment in ExcitingStory class
git commit -a -m "Fix code alignment correctly"

Create a new commit which adds a few notes on Changelog_theosotr file
git commit -m "Additions on Changelog_theosotr file"

Push branch 'theosotr' to the upstream repository
git push origin theosotr

Go to master branch
git checkout master

Merge branch 'theosotr' into master branch
git merge theosotr

Push changes to the upstream repository
git push origin master
